{
  "id": "digital-crease",
  "name": "Digital Crease",
  "category": "geometric",
  "url": "shaders/digital-crease.wgsl",
  "description": "Paper-fold creases radiate from center with depth-curve distortion. Temporal persistence simulates paper memory. Chromatic folding separates R/B channels per crease. Audio modulates fold amplitude.",
